
to build the Cromer-Lieberman shared library:

 Win32: 
    > use_mingw   (may need tweaking to point to your installation of MinGW and Msys)
    > copy Mk.win32 Mk.config
    > make install
 
 Mac OSX: 
    # may need to tweak Mk.macosx to point to your gfortran installation
    > cp Mk.macosx Mk.config
    > make install
 
 Linux:
    > cp Mk.linux Mk.config
    > make install

